<br>
Give me a fucking break!  Why not just make it where all players start level 50 and get it over with.  What the fuck is the point of learning the game while you level?  <br>
<br>
The game is already a hell of a lot easier to level to 50 in than it was three years ago because of better equipment available at cheaper prices.  Having a lammy at level 20 now is nothing out of the ordinary, whereas 3 years ago weapons with that damage/delay ratio didn't even exist in the game.<br>
<br>
It's getting to the point that you can be a fucking retard and make it to high levels.  Its a form of socialism being applied to EQ.  EQ is about competition not socialism.  If I wanted socialism I'd go back to the fucking real world where stupid people try and leech off those with brains and motivation. <p><center>
